summary: Hi, my name is Nadine van der Heijden and I am 22 years old. I'm studying Art History at Leiden University and I have done Honours College at the faculty of Archeology. I will be moving to Paris in the beginning of January to finish my bachelor at the Sorbonne. Through my internship by Museum Beelden aan Zee and my board year at Stukafest Leiden, I found out that I am really passionate about the acquisition in the cultural field. Take a look and contact me if you want to learn more about me. Hopefully see you soon :)
